author: The Wall Street Journal
description:
Former Microsoft CEO and philanthropist Bill Gates spoke to WSJ about a recent meeting with Donald Trump, Elon Musk’s DOGE, U.S.-China relations and his upcoming book, “Source Code,” in which he reveals new details about his childhood including his thoughts on the autism spectrum. 

#BillGates #Autism #Shorts
title: Bill Gates on the Autism Spectrum: “That Became a Strength”
